# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.4.0] - 2023-10-15
- Change spa light buttton to a dropdown list of color options
- Call the light circuit on, before changing the color.  Expect the color to be for the correct light this way.

## [1.3.0] - 2023-10-14
- Change pool light buttton and color selector buttons to a dropdown list of color options

## [1.2.0] - 2022-10-03
- Add buttons to scroll through pool light colors

## [1.1.0] - 2022-08-07
- Make IP_ADDR and environment variable

## [1.0.0] - 2022-07-17
- Initial release
